      _TV Show Notes_ 
      ===============----------------------------------------------------
                                   
       The chefs compete for a place in the final three. They cook at
       Gidleigh Park under the supervision of Michael Caines before 
       preparing a dish in the MasterChef Kitchen for the scrutiny of
       Gregg Wallace and Michel Roux Jnr 

